{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e95370bc23","title":"姚文元在广播大楼门口接见革命师生谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2bd14e943c","index":0,"year":1966,"month":11,"day":2,"articleId":"e95370bc23","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"新闻广播和出版","id":"268718f23b","type":"主题"},{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"姚文元","id":"92a8a42842","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"yaowenyuan","name":"姚文元文录","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"姚文元","files":"/books/姚文元文录.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"45f848c5df","name":"姚文元"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8d577d7892","type":"title","text":"姚文元在广播大楼门口接见革命师生谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"224faeb94c","type":"paragraph","text":"〖姚文元同志由广院学生和广播局战斗团的同志陪同，从大楼里出来，冒着寒冷的夜风在大门院子里接见了革命师生。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"094704c8d5","type":"paragraph","text":"同学喊：同学们！姚文元同志来跟大家见面了！（在场同学及广播局战斗团同志热烈鼓掌欢呼。）","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bab612fc37","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：同学们！我们是来支持你们革命的！","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8127de86e6","type":"paragraph","text":"（有的同学跟姚文元同志握手，同学们纷纷向姚文元同志谈学院的情况。）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e859785d4d","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：广播学院的情况我们有所了解……。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f02349b5bf","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们几次来向他们（丁莱夫派的工作组）要黑材料，他们不给！","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35f0ead5b9","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：广播学院不仅是黑材料问题，还有别的问题。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"51cb710379","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：姚文元同志，您不知道学院现在的情况……","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e2a8249b9e","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：广播学院不是贴了我们的大字报吗？我们怎么不知道呢？不是有人还要造江青同志的反吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"962ae85f8e","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：姚文元同志，希望你们到我们学院来了解情况。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"045775b019","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：我们是要去的，不过现在没有时间。同学们！跟大家商量一下：你们留下几个代表，我们一起来处理今天这个事，今天时间已经很晚了，我看其余的同学都回去，大家同意不同意？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1913b866bd","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：好！同意！","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a55fc4b2a","type":"paragraph","text":"爬在门上的同学喊：姚文元同志！我们要进来！你要他们让我们进来！姚文元同志与警卫人员商量，这时，王寿仁同志趋前，姚跟王寿仁同志商量：是不是让他们进来？","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"293c796350","type":"paragraph","text":"王：（对负责警卫的同志）那就让他们进来吧。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"58a735f9a1","type":"paragraph","text":"大门打开了。门外的同学们雄赳赳气昂昂地走进大门，与在大楼内的同学汇合，而后就纷纷上车。战斗团的一位女同志对姚文元同志说：希望中央文革也关心广播局的运动情况。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ca79ed9a9","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：好，好，这些事我们以后再谈。你们也要支持他们的行动嘛1","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"86e4259e5c","type":"paragraph","text":"战斗团的女同志答：我们是支持的。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a434ab3409","type":"paragraph","text":"这时，汽车开动了，广播学院的革命师生唱着革命歌曲，乘车离开大楼返校，姚文元同志鼓掌挥手送走了革命小将。","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3a16bf8bcd","type":"paragraph","text":"谈话中，姚文元同志还对警卫部队和革命小将双方做了思想工作。姚文元同志对小将们说：你们不要责怪他们（指警卫部队），他们是执行任务。姚文元同志后来对警卫部队说：你们要理解他们（指小将们）的心情，要理解他们的行动。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"030c338f18","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：我们几次来向他们（丁莱夫派的工作组）要黑材料，他们不给！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09d295b790","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：广播学院不是贴了我们的大字报吗？我们怎么不知道呢？不是有人还要造江青同志的反吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c28cb5271","type":"paragraph","text":"〖姚文元同志由广院学生和广播局战斗团的同志陪同，从大楼里出来，冒着寒冷的夜风在大门院子里接见了革命师生。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0d81b28fa3","type":"paragraph","text":"同学：好！同意！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0fd41fd268","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：同学们！我们是来支持你们革命的！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"154a6d1eb8","type":"paragraph","text":"姚：广播学院的情况我们有所了解……。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"17ecdb145b","type":"paragraph","text":"大门打开了。门外的同学们雄赳赳气昂昂地走进大门，与在大楼内的同学汇合，而后就纷纷上车。战斗团的一位女同志对姚文元同志说：希望中央文革也关心广播局的运动情况。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e95370bc23","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id